===Transitive verb===
{{en-verb|diffus|ing}}

#To [[spread]] over or through as in [[air]], [[water]], or other matter, especially by [[fluid]] [[motion]] or [[passive]] means.
#:''Food coloring '''diffuses''' in water''

====Derived terms====
*[[diffuser]]

===Adjective===
'''diffuse''' ({{compar}} '''more diffuse''', {{superl}} '''most diffuse''')
#Everywhere or throughout everything; not [[focus]]ed or [[concentrate]]d.
#:''Such a '''diffuse''' effort is unlikely to produce good results.''

